    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've taken what seems like an easy task: find missing keys to unlock doors that will lead you to secrets of the abyss. What you don't know is the danger that lurks in the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/b804940e0f12ea4a14f893d5ac283105.poster.avif?t=1750958883\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/b804940e0f12ea4a14f893d5ac283105.webm?t=1750958883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all 6 keys to unlock the hidden door, find secret notes that will provide you with mysterious story and reveal all the secrets that the house holds! Listen to Crooked Man sounds, be aware of your surroundings, but DO NOT LOOK AT HIM!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNCOVER ALL THE SECRETS</strong> by collecting pieces of evidence and putting them together, making sense of what is happening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/2595b72967ed70218ba83e9a247b67a4.poster.avif?t=1750958883\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/2595b72967ed70218ba83e9a247b67a4.webm?t=1750958883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>YOU NEVER KNOW WHAT LIES AHEAD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you delve deeper into the exploration, you uncover unsettling truths about what is really going on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/a7b2ec40cae17ea3e2289386b612b9ce.poster.avif?t=1750958883\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/a7b2ec40cae17ea3e2289386b612b9ce.webm?t=1750958883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE UNKNOWN, OR BECOME A PART OF THE LEGEND</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/f421bfc2859c7bff2838c093f78fa70f.webp?t=1750958883\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/f421bfc2859c7bff2838c093f78fa70f.poster.webp?t=1750958883\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=184 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >immersive and intense gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional Collectables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphical Settings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Checkpoint Save</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic Shooting Mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/d4f370474c9c58b43e5e9f6f013f5437.webp?t=1750958883\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241480/extras/d4f370474c9c58b43e5e9f6f013f5437.poster.webp?t=1750958883\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=184 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>CREDITS:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lead Programmer / Director:</strong> Matija Cerovac</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D Artist / Animations:</strong> Matija Bogović</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Producer / Sound Designer:</strong> Rudolf Ravbar</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music Composer</strong>: Vito Mamula</p>",
